It's been our home for a little over 2 years and we love it, we'll leave a list of our favorite local spots :) Cozy, charming apartment with 1 full bed, full kitchen (fridge, oven, stove, all dishes), living room (w/ TV and couch) full bathroom (w/ shower/tub). It's the perfect spot to make your home while you explore NY! Also enjoy the chalkboard wall (chalk provided). You'll have access to the entire space: bedroom, living room, kitchen, bathroom! Quiet, safe neighborhood home to lots of families. Apartment is located next to an elementary school so kids and parents will be coming / going during the daytime hours.
